                <h2 class="font-heading mt-10 scroll-m-28 text-xl font-medium tracking-tight lg:mt-12" id="api-reference">API Reference</h2>

                <h3 class="font-heading mt-8 scroll-m-28 text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Avatar</h3>
                <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">The <code>Avatar</code> component is the root component that wraps the avatar image and fallback.</p>
                <div class="no-scrollbar my-6 w-full overflow-x-auto overflow-y-hidden rounded-xl border">
                    <table class="relative w-full min-w-max overflow-hidden border-none text-sm">
                        <thead><tr class="m-0 border-b"><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-bold">Prop</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-bold">Type</th><th class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-bold">Default</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody class="[&_tr:last-child]:border-b-0">
                            <tr class="m-0 border-b"><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap"><code class="bg-muted relative rounded-md px-[0.3rem] py-[0.2rem] font-mono text-[0.8rem] whitespace-nowrap">Size</code></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap"><code class="bg-muted relative rounded-md px-[0.3rem] py-[0.2rem] font-mono text-[0.8rem] whitespace-nowrap">"default" | "sm" | "lg"</code></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap">"default"</td></tr>
                            <tr class="m-0 border-b"><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap"><code class="bg-muted relative rounded-md px-[0.3rem] py-[0.2rem] font-mono text-[0.8rem] whitespace-nowrap">Class</code></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap"><code class="bg-muted relative rounded-md px-[0.3rem] py-[0.2rem] font-mono text-[0.8rem] whitespace-nowrap">string</code></td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-left whitespace-nowrap">-</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>

